<s> Bausch & Lomb Inc. said its pharmaceuticals subsidiary agreed to supply collagen corneal shields for animal eye surgery to a unit of International Minerals & Chemical Corp . </s>
<s> Terms were n't disclosed . </s>
<s> The agreement marks Bausch & Lomb 's first venture selling its eye care products for use by veterinarians . </s>
<s> The collagen corneal shield helps speed healing of the cornea after eye surgery . </s>
<s> The product will be distributed by Pitman-Moore Inc. , a subsidiary of International Minerals . </s>
